1. Các khái niệm cơ bản của OOP
1. Basic concept of OOP
OOP based on 4 principle:
    1. Encapsulation (Tính đóng gói): hide implementation detail inside the object and providing only the necessaly interface
    2. Inheritance (Tính kế thừa): a class can inherit the properties and method form another class
    3. Polymorphism (Tính đa hình): Objects form another class can call the same method but the behavior is different
    4. Abtriaction (Tính trừu tượng): Show only the necessary details and hide the complicated details

